data.description: Are you searching for a spectacular home to celebrate the holidays, look no further! This exceptional property boasts numerous features, including open concept, double ovens, first floor master with a luxurious custom closet, an inviting eat in kitchen, and  a formal dining room. Additionally, there are built in speakers in the front room. Don't miss this opportunity to live in the Jack Britt school district. Custom closet and all rooms upstairs have new paint. Schedule your showing today!Seller is offering $2,000.00 towards closing cost. Preferred Lender is Casey Whealton with American Security mortgage. Preferred lender is offering $2,000.00 towards closing cost. Contact her for more details 910-644-9963. For questions or concerns call the listing agent Micaela Keel 910-778-6398. Keller Williams or listing agent does not hold EMD.
